description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a full time Personal Assistant for our management team; this is on a fixed term basis for 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who can provide support to the General Manager and the Human Resources Manager, no experience is necessary although the ideal person will be able to learn quickly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role offers the opportunity to work in primary care with our multi disciplinary team. If you are organised and have a keen willingness to learn on the job in a fast paced environment then we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You need to be a good communicator and be able to work autonomously but also as part of a team. The ability to multi task and cope with day to day distractions that come with this role in a busy practice is important.&lt;/p&gt;
